  楊  挺  宏\r\n本件正本證明與原本無異\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　 111　　年　　3 　　月　　29　　日\r\n                              書記官  林  敬  展","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TYDM/111%2c%e6%a1%83%e7%b0%a1%2c764%2c20220504%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TYDM,111,桃簡,764,20220504,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"桃簡","JNO":"764","JDATE":"20220504","JTITLE":"竊盜"}